審訊時態度互相交替<br />\n<br />\n30.交換：<br />\n審問人員請求嫌疑人跟他交換訊息。<br />\n例子「我需要你的幫助，我給你一點，你給我一點」<br />\n<br />\n31.模仿動作：<br />\n審問人員嘗試模仿嫌疑人的動作，例如雙腳交疊。目的是想令嫌疑人的潛意識認為對方是跟他站在同一陣線。<br />\n<br />\n32.等待：<br />\n審訊前要求嫌疑人等待，令嫌疑人長時間獨自處於未知的恐懼當中，藉此折磨嫌疑人的心智。<br />\n<br />\n33.相信：<br />\n審問人員的態度傾向於相信嫌疑人，令嫌疑人以為自己的話被認可，其實只是審問人員配合你演戲。只會讓處於對抗心理的嫌疑人放下戒備，審問人員亦會在嫌疑人沒有防備時進攻。<br />\n<br />\n34.話鋒一轉：<br />\n配合「相信」，讓嫌疑人放下戒備時突然出其不意地進攻，這種突然的情況會令嫌疑人一時腦袋空白，想不到怎樣解釋。<br />\n例子：審問人員觀察到嫌疑人有受傷，在嫌疑人放下戒備時突然問他「你的傷怎麼了？」<br />\n<br />\n35.感情牌：<br />\n例子1「如果你還在這樣，你怎樣面對你的家人？朋友？」<br />\n例子2「你知不知道為什麼我那麼在意這名女孩？因為我也有女兒，年紀還是差不多。你不說真話會令我很心痛，拜托你快點講真話。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:30:27.000Z","msg":"有料到"},{"pid":"55a80e618c8e05aeb5ec38123d727f239be0a710","tid":2415454,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T09:51:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a22595be12c9f891774f4b40fe63bcc8f73ede36","tid":2415454,"uid":335883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:36:50.000Z","msg":"上 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2409430/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2409430/page/1</a><br />\n中 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2411565/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2411565/page/1</a><br />\n下 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2415454/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2415454/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"c868255277c0c17c7e5ad8765980ed5092902004","tid":2415454,"uid":303298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實入到狗竇合埋眼一句都唔答係唔係一個好嘅處理方法？"},{"pid":"5f6e204140ed1020e1f5a31b4efc220a7789b8e6","tid":2415454,"uid":392507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c868255277c0c17c7e5ad8765980ed5092902004","tid":2415454,"uid":303298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實入到狗竇合埋眼一句都唔答係唔係一個好嘅處理方法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"可以參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zqHet9iQQAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzqHet9iQQAI&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=1aecc8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zqHet9iQQAI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/afKU6-rl7z0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FafKU6-rl7z0&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=4c0b713a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/afKU6-rl7z0</a><br />\n要記得幾個重點<br />\n1.唔好透露任何嘢，傾閑偈都係<br />\n2.除咗姓名、年齡、身分證號碼、職業之外，其他一律唔好講<br />\n3.警察唔係朋友，而係敵人<br />\n4.可以表示唔舒服、要求入醫院。如果喺唔舒服嘅情況下落口供，法庭係唔會接納份口供<br />\n5.要求見律師/父母<br />\n6.要認識多啲相關嘅法律，唔好畀警察唆擺"},{"pid":"4637efecd6a4d37fb57f153b0e913ae51b36423f","tid":2415454,"uid":40521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOGJOBMw.png&amp;h=731371ce&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"5b395ad79775402cc5f8a30f5571685f21028ea6","tid":2415454,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc442d0bad8666a6eb18d4fc4d801254388466c9","tid":2415454,"uid":207596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:37:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"36ad45761cfbe3a70605e7b6aa7570b41090c483","tid":2415454,"uid":367090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:42:22.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdbcc1a272f602fd6afff8120e6f2f53ea99c8c","tid":2415454,"uid":61282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5f6e204140ed1020e1f5a31b4efc220a7789b8e6","tid":2415454,"uid":392507,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c868255277c0c17c7e5ad8765980ed5092902004","tid":2415454,"uid":303298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"其實入到狗竇合埋眼一句都唔答係唔係一個好嘅處理方法？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"可以參考吓<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/zqHet9iQQAI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FzqHet9iQQAI&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=1aecc8d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/zqHet9iQQAI</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/afKU6-rl7z0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FafKU6-rl7z0&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkgzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=4c0b713a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/afKU6-rl7z0</a><br />\n要記得幾個重點<br />\n1.唔好透露任何嘢，傾閑偈都係<br />\n2.除咗姓名、年齡、身分證號碼、職業之外，其他一律唔好講<br />\n3.警察唔係朋友，而係敵人<br />\n4.可以表示唔舒服、要求入醫院。如果喺唔舒服嘅情況下落口供，法庭係唔會接納份口供<br />\n5.要求見律師/父母<br />\n6.要認識多啲相關嘅法律，唔好畀警察唆擺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T11:52:40.000Z","msg":"啲死差佬目的永遠只有一個，唔係查明真相，而係入鳩你"},{"pid":"696f7ca34b13f2c9bad67f1a118079705c95ad9d","tid":2415454,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8df2471d9e1706542d9915a1a8a1b6a4d5e66159","tid":2415454,"uid":216592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T13:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44cdbe302c88901bb937e19d9d1ea2186fcd1d2e","tid":2415454,"uid":350524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:50:26.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5c4cfea54780e9196f3ebdcac4f2b3bc2cc81788","tid":2415454,"uid":350524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"thank you for sharing<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e678a45c3038c43112a80a579d205c33ea492739","tid":2415454,"uid":114781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477c5f8abe90115b37e694f26ab5bbfffd93e4f6","tid":2415454,"uid":74598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T02:55:42.000Z","msg":"留"},{"pid":"d1dcdc3784bbe01d58bbd3f300363b78d3674286","tid":2415454,"uid":201470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T03:40:25.000Z","msg":"推"}]}